1. Select the account to use for your deposit.

3. Sign the back of your check and write "For Mobile Deposit at Wells Fargo Bank Only" below your signature. (Or if available, check the box that reads: "Check here if mobile deposit".)
4. Take a photo of the front and back of your endorsed check.
